              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_7131_step_1_11",
                "text": "<span style='color: red;'><b style='color: red;'> Warning:</b> Installation of the thermostat must be done by a qualified electrician.</span> \n<br><br>\nRefer to the device's User Manual for instructions on installation and electric connections.\n<br><br>\nTo avoid risk of electric shock, make sure to turn off the power before beginning installation. \n<br><br>\nOnce your Thermostat has been installed and mounted, press the 'Next' button below to continue."
              }
